{
  "id": "RAW_43441ec1",
  "title": "一只大头机器狗供不应求，打响了消费级具身智能第一枪",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2025/12/366060.html",
  "date": "2025-12-26 12:59:00",
  "author": "贾浩楠",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"91\">贾浩楠 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"92\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"2\">没想到2025行至年末，具身智能赛道仍然抓紧最后的窗口带给我们惊喜：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5c9cd42b188b40879ab6e125d9bc25e4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Ddo1Q9zrJ%2B9FSaE9pxFLbxUe8Fk%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5c9cd42b188b40879ab6e125d9bc25e4~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Ddo1Q9zrJ%2B9FSaE9pxFLbxUe8Fk%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"3\">这只名叫大头BoBo的超能机器狗，不光赚了眼球：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/520dfaa45fef47ea96f4fc5323164c92~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=m9CEEovQ558KYYJauM%2FeDHWqplc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/520dfaa45fef47ea96f4fc5323164c92~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=m9CEEovQ558KYYJauM%2FeDHWqplc%3D\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"4\">还上了热搜：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/419859a2affc44d08b9ceae9fa1170fe~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=st%2FlOfh56a%2Fwl8WQ9aSLFa8OiiU%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/419859a2affc44d08b9ceae9fa1170fe~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=st%2FlOfh56a%2Fwl8WQ9aSLFa8OiiU%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"5\">并且顺手刷了一个行业纪录：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/31516c984d5a4e2381d34322c72bd11a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bczvZ%2BMx2pc7xkzg8f8lil58eHI%3D\" data-src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/31516c984d5a4e2381d34322c72bd11a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bczvZ%2BMx2pc7xkzg8f8lil58eHI%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"6\">售价不到一万块的Vbot超能机器狗大头BoBo，52分钟内订出1000台。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"7\">人形、四足全算上，从来没有任何一个产品能像大头BoBo这样收获大家真金白银的喜爱。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"8\">具身智能元年，消费级具身智能赛道跑出了现象级“第一品牌”——Vbot维他动力。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"10\">Vbot超能机器狗正式发布开卖大概5个小时后，“维他动力机器狗定价9988元”的话题直接被网友推上了热搜：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/879561d0aea440248a655919e7cd5cca~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=5N6CyICf32jBxmjluzDAG45AhRM%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/879561d0aea440248a655919e7cd5cca~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=5N6CyICf32jBxmjluzDAG45AhRM%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">价格不算便宜，但依然挡不住大家的热情：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/011c77185f3946739355b9ff8c493a3b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=gPmP1RqGkNY3XZdjlQVb9TgCSqQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/011c77185f3946739355b9ff8c493a3b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=gPmP1RqGkNY3XZdjlQVb9TgCSqQ%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"12\">有人秀订单催Vbot维他动力交货，顺便求蹭一个公测资格：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/601c7263e2904fdcaab0212c9868daa2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=e2EYnlVlz2jdN4GfogedKTu5dfQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/601c7263e2904fdcaab0212c9868daa2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=e2EYnlVlz2jdN4GfogedKTu5dfQ%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"13\">多说一句，过几天Vbot维他动力官方第一批公测，500台不收费，优先已经付了定金的用户。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"14\">还有网友给大头BoBo穿搭支招：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e3aab43c79e84e09a7ee28018002dfda~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=6kKQl51J6Fn1vYuCP7olAcgc5Y0%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e3aab43c79e84e09a7ee28018002dfda~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=6kKQl51J6Fn1vYuCP7olAcgc5Y0%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"15\">更多的网友，已经期待起了大头BoBo成为家里孩子最亲密的伙伴：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8313754112bf4bb193e3dceb3f32bca2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2F8SttNwRSmClCvpRjPWTqre86ag%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8313754112bf4bb193e3dceb3f32bca2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2F8SttNwRSmClCvpRjPWTqre86ag%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"16\">真金白银下单买了大头BoBo的用户，纷纷晒起了订单：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/56648edaa7f447d4a1c4f02004c11c06~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=cU8IQVBMKN3FlenKOd19KVozEmc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/56648edaa7f447d4a1c4f02004c11c06~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=cU8IQVBMKN3FlenKOd19KVozEmc%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c3ca123d68684a91b9d8ab2f0693fb4b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=LANcQKcC9DJmO2O%2FQgvsgvq5OFY%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c3ca123d68684a91b9d8ab2f0693fb4b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=LANcQKcC9DJmO2O%2FQgvsgvq5OFY%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"17\">这其中还有量子位观众熟悉的AI行业大咖，比如001号用户<strong>余凯</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/873aa69582234cd5a2f661205b9ceb3b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=QHZev1fvcymIXtg0rlFMm%2F8vQJk%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/873aa69582234cd5a2f661205b9ceb3b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=QHZev1fvcymIXtg0rlFMm%2F8vQJk%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"18\">002号用户<strong>余轶南</strong>：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/01bdab706cc94d39a41861ecbd0a40d2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=oD7UUKglc1CMxgdoCNmtEdmYqDs%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/01bdab706cc94d39a41861ecbd0a40d2~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=oD7UUKglc1CMxgdoCNmtEdmYqDs%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"19\">不过我举报，余轶南是动用“特权”抢的002号订单，毕竟他就是Vbot维他动力创始人本人…这边建议余总明年3月正式交付的时候，给焦急的普通用户让出排队序号（手动狗头）。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"20\">大头BoBo，可谓从普通用户火到了AI科技圈。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"21\">别看1000台的数据不像车企动不动几万台那么高，但在消费级机器人这个赛道，已经创造历史了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"22\">毕竟消费级四足机器狗市场，处在刚刚起步的“萌芽”期，至于人形产品，甚至还处在“概念期”，不足以称为“市场”。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/91db6fc152af49b6a2f4abaf76a6a74d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2F09Z0QTbrOGGBGPzQ8HashiP9pQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/91db6fc152af49b6a2f4abaf76a6a74d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2F09Z0QTbrOGGBGPzQ8HashiP9pQ%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"23\">目前最好的消费级四足机器狗销量纪录，是一年时间在全球范围卖出2万台左右：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c1cd7bc64832420eb91a847ae2f3523b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2FTj4LZJvyvJYMk1GofseW3nTrmw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c1cd7bc64832420eb91a847ae2f3523b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=%2FTj4LZJvyvJYMk1GofseW3nTrmw%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"24\">售价9988元的的大头BoBo，妥妥的消费级价格，旗舰机配置。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"25\">销量、价格、反馈等等维度综合来看，Vbot维他动力的大头BoBo出道即巅峰。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"26\">大头BoBo为啥会这么受欢迎呢？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"27\">如果你是硬科技发烧友，长期追踪体验相关产品的话，肯定能发现市面上常见的消费级四足机器人，大多是根据成熟的工业级产品改装、“简配”而来，造型设计直接继承了“生猛刚硬”的姿态，交互上也只有简单的跟随、跑跳。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"28\">大头BoBo则是一种之前完全没见过的产品。有其他四足机器人有的一切，包括运动、承重、跟随等等能力。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/1be43f5baecf44f6b6b35cead51af6e5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=lyEv%2BYaWLpzY%2FF84J7AsUmJcrQ0%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/1be43f5baecf44f6b6b35cead51af6e5~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=lyEv%2BYaWLpzY%2FF84J7AsUmJcrQ0%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"29\">但同时又有其他产品身上从未见过的<strong>亲和力</strong>，比如丰富的“面部表情”、肢体动作：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/970efdd9648d4719aaf97b7025efad7e~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=8lSle%2BJ05W7cpT94h6M8muD3FIE%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/970efdd9648d4719aaf97b7025efad7e~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=8lSle%2BJ05W7cpT94h6M8muD3FIE%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"30\">当然也有实用功能，比如轻度负重：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e29e03a892564aafa0f4c778904491f7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=sdDyPH9SuWMDwJLAA8cstLlXAvw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/e29e03a892564aafa0f4c778904491f7~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=sdDyPH9SuWMDwJLAA8cstLlXAvw%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"31\">背后的行业首个全场景空间基座模型，使得BoBo在基础的语音助手能力之外，能够理解、执行复杂任务。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"32\">比如你可以告诉它：“去把家里的宝宝叫醒”，大头BoBo会先理解，宝宝是谁，宝宝在哪，然后规划路线：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c198615b6070475ca726dd94d9a96c39~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=82Bx1tUvQmVh7hcp%2FmJ0JPNs2bk%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c198615b6070475ca726dd94d9a96c39~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=82Bx1tUvQmVh7hcp%2FmJ0JPNs2bk%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"33\">一位已经下单的网友一语道破大头BoBo受欢迎的“天机”：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f492660ed06e4203a4b1c12421f4bc7f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=nk9myi7hVGv8tG4LyIbjkyXAOeo%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/f492660ed06e4203a4b1c12421f4bc7f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=nk9myi7hVGv8tG4LyIbjkyXAOeo%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"35\">领先技术体系、超强产品定义、再加上出色的设计，是大头BoBo出道即巅峰的核心原因。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"36\"><strong>比如技术层面</strong>，大头BoBo是目前多模态大模型、AI Agent、具身智能硬件等等集大成之作。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"37\">内置地瓜S100P芯片，整体算力达128TOPS，是迄今为止消费级量产机器人的最高算力。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a0de09ec62554741940402455b45d048~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=mxGbnz4qzWw6rtvI%2Bg78ZUJTNk4%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a0de09ec62554741940402455b45d048~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=mxGbnz4qzWw6rtvI%2Bg78ZUJTNk4%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"38\">续航问题上，电量达到近600Wh，较行业上限提升了37.5%，续航3-5小时，不至于“牵着出来抱着回去”。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"39\">认知与运动能力，Vbot维他动力不同于任何侧重于机器人本体或通用大模型的公司，而是设计了一套全新全场景空间基座模型：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/72a1b04c40754cc7b26b0626d33ab4be~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=xVAmTz%2B2PNcZvBxZXweZFArkQcE%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/72a1b04c40754cc7b26b0626d33ab4be~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=xVAmTz%2B2PNcZvBxZXweZFArkQcE%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"40\">Vbot维他动力的的Agent架构，<strong>抛开遥控器和预设的程序指令</strong>&nbsp;，核心是视觉—语言—行动（V-L-A）模型 ，统一了<strong>看懂—听懂—做对—解释清楚</strong>的全链路 。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"41\">用户通过自然语言给出指令后，Agent大脑会利用思维链（CoT）和反思（Reflection）等机制，像产品经理一样理解意图、拆解任务，然后调度各种工具来完成 。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"42\">这些工具不仅包括机器人自身的感知和技能，还包括可扩展的物理世界工具（如通过多功能背板连接机械臂或运动相机）和互联网服务 。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"43\">前面提到的大头BoBo“叫醒宝宝”的任务，核心能力就是VLA基座模型+Agent架构。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/b97b465401cf4232b6d44ab794355047~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=tuPGtEmp0TQtBfWo9n1aMZpGqVM%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/b97b465401cf4232b6d44ab794355047~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=tuPGtEmp0TQtBfWo9n1aMZpGqVM%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"44\"><strong>其次是大头BoBo产品定义超强</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"45\">机器人进家服务、陪护的场景，可能没人比Vbot维他动力想得更清楚明白。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"46\">技术上，多模态大模型、世界模型等等有“终局”潜力的具身智能AI大脑技术，还在起步研发阶段，这就使得人形产品保证不了住宅空间内高精度高可靠性的要求。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"47\">用户层面，如果你是父母的话，<strong>买一个身形、力量都比家里小朋友大得多的人形机器人回家，还要留他们独处，是不是很不放心？</strong></p>\n  <p data-track=\"48\"><strong>所以现阶段，Vbot维他动力认定形态、交互上，和普通宠物最接近的四足机器狗，是消费级具身智能的最佳选择</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"49\">场景选择直击用户刚需痛点——带娃哄娃；</p>\n  <p data-track=\"50\">又从用户体验角度出发选择了合适的产品形态——四足机器狗；</p>\n  <p data-track=\"51\">再从实际的使用场景，比如家庭环境中的自由移动、陪玩交互等等需求出发，匹配了合适的技术体系VLA和Agent架构。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a984bc4688b04a698293bdf365a6254d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=MPr4upwLKA0VMj25bN88bSToikw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a984bc4688b04a698293bdf365a6254d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=MPr4upwLKA0VMj25bN88bSToikw%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"52\">在AI和具身智能的推进中，提供实实在在的生产力价值，可能还达不到量产开售水平。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"53\">但如果是一个“情绪价值”为主，能一起成长的“小朋友玩伴”，那一切就大为不同了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"54\">大头BoBo是消费级具身智能赛道，第一个让用户愿意接受一定的容错度，更愿意共同成长的产品。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"55\">最后是大头BoBo的从设计、到命名，再到交互设计都极其出众。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"56\"><strong>整体遵循迪士尼动画12法则</strong>，通过预期、时间控制、夸张等动画原则，让机器狗的转头、停顿、目光都带有情感逻辑。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"57\">比如交互模式借鉴了《超能陆战队》里的“大白”，表情和声音，则借鉴了「瓦力」风格，天然带萌感。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"58\">没有之前机器狗的“赛博感”，温暖友善的体验，瞬间拉近了与用户（尤其是家庭中的孩子和女性）的心理距离。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/4cd1783ee6124a199d9b257da0f67d7a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=XN6ib1lIFUGbTH7%2BXm%2FiwsbowGQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/4cd1783ee6124a199d9b257da0f67d7a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=XN6ib1lIFUGbTH7%2BXm%2FiwsbowGQ%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"59\"><strong>四足机器狗做出“狗味”，既有情绪价值，又不是花架子，真正具备承担任务的能力</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"60\">直击<strong>中产带娃哄娃</strong>的需求痛点，<strong>第一次让普通用户看见、体验消费级机器人的价值</strong>。\n   <br class=\"sysbr\">\n   这是Vbot维他动力原生家庭机器人产品思路，对工业级产品“减配”的降维打击。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"62\">去年圣诞节，Vbot维他动力才刚刚注册成立，仅一年时间交卷获得的反馈和订单成绩，超出了官方预期，也超出了外界预期。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"63\">消费级四足机器狗，突破了以往以展示、获客、表演价值为主的价值局限，首次具备了被个人用户认可和接受的情感陪护与生活辅助价值。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"64\">可以说Vbot维他动力第一次开创了<strong>家庭机器人</strong>这个品类。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"65\">当然火爆订单之下，敏捷迅速的用户服务也得跟上：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5d7d983ae638456c92acfcc57852169d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=MUwVuTwaFgHs7Dr2t%2BdnDJgRwIA%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/5d7d983ae638456c92acfcc57852169d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=MUwVuTwaFgHs7Dr2t%2BdnDJgRwIA%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"66\">创始团队，已经“卷铺盖睡工厂了”。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"67\">大头BoBo开门红，是选对了品类，又把合适的技术在合适的时间用在了合适的场景里。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"68\"><strong>其诞生，与IBM 1980年第一台个人计算机5150横空出世极其相似</strong>：</p>\n  <p data-track=\"69\">前沿黑科技，从庞大、笨拙的工业场景落地方案，变成轻巧、便捷，能提供情绪价值和日常任务处理的个人消费品。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"70\">一样是在底层彻底重塑产品思路，上层彻底变革普通人生活方式、工作效率。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"71\">唯一的不同，是技术驱动因素，从半个世纪前的大规模集成电路，变成如今的多模态AI大模型。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"72\"><strong>一个普通用户愿意接受、愿意付费的具身“消费级”时代，真的要来了</strong>。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6d1a03021927491e8cb7ef7816d566fc~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=AYL5EShhun4Tk6jXaM%2BgOKGszdQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6d1a03021927491e8cb7ef7816d566fc~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=AYL5EShhun4Tk6jXaM%2BgOKGszdQ%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"73\">Vbot维他动力发布第一款产品之前，具身智能玩家的技术分化大致有两个趋势，一种是强硬件玩家，产品以各种形态、成本的机器人本体为主，销售给不同需求的场景方。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"74\">另一种玩家则是更偏重模型算法，试图给具身智能打造认知理解世界万物的通用智能。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"75\">这个赛道，又能细分出主攻认知“大脑”和运动“小脑”两类玩家。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"76\">这也就造成了眼下具身智能产品无论是演示还是落地，最常见的模式是先花钱买一个本体，再找另外的AI公司根据场景任务定制算法软件。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"77\">或者更常见于各种机器人运动会、制造业流水线上的场景：干脆买个机器人本体，然后用遥控器背后的“人”来完成各种任务。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"78\">真的是“有多少人工，就有多少智能”了……</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a6e8f89966e948469cca00bfead87328~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bfYI0umfkJKWK5ZuDdcD5u6DGPc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a6e8f89966e948469cca00bfead87328~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=bfYI0umfkJKWK5ZuDdcD5u6DGPc%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"79\">无论偏重软硬哪种路线，都有底层的死循环解不了：<strong>没AI大脑能力，具身智能命题本身就不存在</strong>，而<strong>只有模型算法没有硬件设计、制造能力，就无法建立高质量数据闭环，迭代路径被锁死</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"80\">从这个角度看，<strong>Vbot维他动力的“无遥控、真智能”</strong>，表面上是使用体验上更加便捷，吸引用户购买使用。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"81\">而日益累积的终端落地数量，又源源不断传回各种复杂场景高价值数据，驱动算法软件快速进化，吸引更多用户购买，进一步扩大硬件规模……</p>\n  <p data-track=\"82\">通向AGI的具身智能“数据飞轮”，不就建立起来了吗？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"83\">从销量数据层面，Vbot维他动力一鸣惊人；</p>\n  <p data-track=\"84\">从家庭陪护机器人底层对安全、情绪的本质需求来看，Vbot维他动力交出首秀成绩，毫无疑问是“消费级具身智能”这个赛道的领跑者。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"85\">而且从真正的落地实践，量产过线标准来看，Vbot维他动力明年3月开始大批量交付，也是率先把这种理念落地实践的玩家。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c4ac276060e34f159d585ac64083f13e~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9D36if55%2FKZjO%2FK%2FrMgyn7MYths%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/c4ac276060e34f159d585ac64083f13e~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20251226205134446B712C7A5751824309&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=9D36if55%2FKZjO%2FK%2FrMgyn7MYths%3D\">\n   <p></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"86\">这也是这个团队展现的综合能力——<strong>把合适的技术在合适的时间用在合适的场景</strong>——在AI技术领域，就是所有玩家一次次被拷问的PMF，Product-Market Fit（产品市场契合度），而真正抓到了PMF金线的团队，势能只会越来越强，雪球会越滚越大，品牌会越来越响亮。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"87\">而且最重要的是，在具身智能机器人轰轰烈烈的元年里，在百花齐放百家争鸣的2025，Vbot维他动力以大头BoBo交卷，用技术、产品和市场反馈，实现了公开检验。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"88\">在消费级具身智能赛道，之前前无古人……获评“消费具身智能第一品牌”，当之无愧。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"89\">或许用不了多少年，具身智能机器人、消费级具身智能机器人，会像如今的智能驾驶、智能汽车一样遍地开花，年交百万，走进每一个寻常百姓家。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"90\">而到时候真正回溯起来，大头BoBo的形象和背后的Vbot维他动力，都会被作为绕不过去的一环，反复提及。</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "量子位报道了消费级具身智能产品 Vbot 超能机器狗“大头 BoBo”在 2025 年末的爆火，其 52 分钟售罄 1000 台的销售成绩，预示着消费级具身智能时代的到来。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "量子位报道了消费级具身智能产品 Vbot 超能机器狗“大头 BoBo”在 2025 年末的爆火，其 52 分钟售罄 1000 台的销售成绩，预示着消费级具身智能时代的到来。",
  "summary": "文章报道了 2025 年末名为“大头 BoBo”的 Vbot 超能机器狗的热销现象，该产品在 52 分钟内订出 1000 台，创下了消费级具身智能赛道的销售记录。文章分析了其受欢迎的原因，包括领先的技术体系（内置地瓜 S100P 芯片，V-L-A 模型和 Agent 架构），超强的产品定义（聚焦家庭陪护场景，选择四足机器狗形态），以及出色的设计（遵循迪士尼动画 12 法则，打造亲和力）。作者认为大头 BoBo 的成功在于填补了消费级具身智能市场的空白，首次将具身智能机器人真正带入家庭场景，并将其与 IBM PC 的诞生相提并论，预示着消费级具身智能时代的到来。文章还探讨了具身智能领域软硬件结合的困境，并指出 Vbot 维他动力通过建立“数据飞轮”有望突破这一瓶颈。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vbot 超能机器狗“大头 BoBo”的销量创造了消费级具身智能机器人市场的新纪录。",
      "explanation": "产品在发售 52 分钟内订出 1000 台，远超行业现有水平，突破了之前消费级机器狗一年的全球销量，显示了市场对消费级具身智能产品的巨大需求和接受度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大头 BoBo 通过技术、产品定义和设计创新，成功激活了消费级具身智能市场。",
      "explanation": "产品内置高性能 AI 芯片，采用 V-L-A 模型和 Agent 架构，具备理解和执行复杂任务的能力；同时，产品形态和交互设计高度亲和，聚焦家庭场景，提供情感价值，解决了传统机器狗“赛博感”和功能单一的问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vbot 维他动力开创了家庭机器人新品类，并有望建立具身智能的“数据飞轮”。",
      "explanation": "通过聚焦家庭陪护场景，提供用户愿意接受的产品，收集高价值的用户数据，反哺算法迭代，形成正向循环，有望打破当前具身智能软硬件发展不平衡的困境。"
